Description:
A simple weather forecasting web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
It uses a weather API to fetch real-time weather data for any city and displays details like temperature, humidity, and wind speed.
The app also uses AI-based logic to improve data handling and user experience.


Technologies Used:
#HTML
#CSS
#JavaScript
#Weather API
#AI-powered logic for data processing


Features:
#Search weather by city name
#Real-time weather updates
#Displays temperature, humidity, and wind speed
#Dynamic weather icons based on conditions
#Responsive and modern UI
#Fast and lightweight
